      <title>特朗普称将宣布一项计划，让美国成为“加密之都”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-says-he-ll-announce-a-plan-to-make-us-the-crypto-capital-of-the-planet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普似乎正在更深入地涉足数字资产世界，他表示将公布计划，确保美国成为“全球加密之都”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-says-he-ll-announce-a-plan-to-make-us-the-crypto-capital-of-the-planet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对每架未全面升级的 F-35 战机扣留 500 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/us-withholding-5-million-for-each-f-35-lacking-full-upgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部的 F-35 项目办公室和洛克希德马丁公司表示，对于每架尚未配备符合规格的先进硬件和软件的 F-35 飞机，五角大楼将向洛克希德马丁公司扣留 500 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/us-withholding-5-million-for-each-f-35-lacking-full-upgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称其修改后的起诉书违反了美国政策。以下是他错在哪里</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-s-claim-justice-department-violated-policy-with-indictment-is-debunked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 正在利用其最新的妨碍选举起诉书重新引发对美国特别检察官的政治偏见投诉，理由是政府的政策是避免在选举前采取可能影响结果的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-s-claim-justice-department-violated-policy-with-indictment-is-debunked</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:05:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国政府不会对罗斯班克油田的气候诉讼提出异议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/uk-government-won-t-challenge-climate-lawsuit-on-rosebank-field</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府不会挑战环保组织以气候原因阻止北海 Jackdaw 和 Rosebank 油气开发项目的法律行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/uk-government-won-t-challenge-climate-lawsuit-on-rosebank-field</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 11:42:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>专家组表示，瑞士必须重新定义传统中立并加强与北约的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/switzerland-told-to-redefine-traditional-neutrality-and-bolster-nato-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个独立小组建议，瑞士应该深化与北约和欧盟的军事合作，增加军备开支，并重新考虑其不结盟地位，这将标志着瑞士大胆背离其长期以来的中立立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/switzerland-told-to-redefine-traditional-neutrality-and-bolster-nato-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 11:36:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
